text: Elke Markwort (born 30 November 1965) is a German rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Berlin
